          <em class="tdbc-h3 tdbc-ink--secondary">Software Engineering life demystified</em>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="tdbc-lead tdbc-ink--gray tdbc-mt-md">
        <span class="tdbc-row">
          <span>A list of articles by <a href="https://dkpathak.me/">DKP</a></span> <a href="https://twitter.com/dkp1903/" class="tdbc-icon-button" aria-label="Twitter">
